README for how to run ralgen to generate UVM register models

Step 1:  Edit ms_regs.ralf to add/edit register definitions
Step 2:  Run this command:  ralgen -uvm -t ms_regs ms_regs.ralf
Step 3:  Manual edits...
             a) comment-out the "import uvm_pkg" line
             b) in vim run this command: %s/build_coverage(UVM_NO_COVERAGE)/ UVM_NO_COVERAGE

